Steps to run program

To run server, just run it as ./server as shown in example. It will just wait for connection from clients.

To run client, give IP address of server as shown in example. In output, it will printf message from server.

Example:

For server program:

[root@localhost 7.sockets]# ./server
New connection accepted


For client program:

[root@localhost 7.sockets]# ./client 127.0.0.1
Hi there!! I accepted your connection
